                <mxCell id="35" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;8. Now the client&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;can access the&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;data of the user&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;from the resource&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;server, with this&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 102, 204));&quot;&gt;accessToken&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="edgeLabel;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];" parent="34" vertex="1" connectable="0">
